{"tid":2263291,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"真係要多謝chill club將豹哥同mag擺埋一齊","createTime":"2020-10-29T19:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T07:30:06.000Z","uid":131278,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d8f708e616cd2d67457936c21ee0703a1c7735ff","tid":2263291,"uid":131278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T19:09:56.000Z","msg":"早幾日睇返嗰集chill club<br />\n齋睇表現豹哥真係贏晒<br />\n可惜豹哥係參加星光大道，但又好彩佢唔係玩巨聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有啲矛盾<br />\n星光大道喺亞視，節目（喺香港）行得太前紅唔起，出道後又冇後台冇dj撐，睇吓姜濤含住嚿飯咁都上到榜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔喺無綫又唔使唱埋啲主題曲垃圾情歌<br />\n之後聽咗吓好多豹哥嘅歌，把聲易認，又試過好多唔同曲風<br />\n印象中佢唔係香港人，但覺得佢堅持做廣東歌，紅唔起戥佢可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2abf6afe90704590b01ae60e361c8ad56dc23d4","tid":2263291,"uid":310637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T19:16:16.000Z","msg":"娛樂人生好好聽都好難唱，但轉唱抒情歌就變得太用力"},{"pid":"28554e6bda1dcf66ba2a0a619aee81ef1f507264","tid":2263291,"uid":202553,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T19:22:08.000Z","msg":"陳蕾真係高質到誇張"},{"pid":"4c31858fd7b4db45496ae1b0dc9eef1511ef88d3","tid":2263291,"uid":228050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T22:41:27.000Z","msg":"今年派台既都好好聽<br />\n但係chill club 無唱到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9105de5333de7316e8085b5922b94b0f193de62d","tid":2263291,"uid":131278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:30:06.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪我覺得佢唔紅啦，幾首歌聽落都係唱住叫自己唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}